	<h1 class="title">旅客朋友们，本次航班是用剩饭剩菜作为燃料的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1091/small/1091.jpg?1416973319" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">何姗 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-02 12:09:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11560/medium/11560.jpg?1436638574" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


